making, technical competence, and crew cooperation\u2014the strongest overall profile is **Candidate\u202fC**. His proven reliability, calm crisis handling, rapid correct decisions, and positive crew atmosphere outweigh his communication\u2011style concerns, especially since the other candidates have either missing reliability evidence or more severe interpersonal issues.\n**Vote:** Candidate C\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
